Package org.alljoyn.bus.ifaces

This package contains various standard AllJoyn interfaces.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
DBusProxyObj The standard org.freedesktop.DBus interface that is implemented by the local AllJoyn daemon.
Introspectable The standard org.freedesktop.DBus.Introspectable interface.
Peer The standard org.freedesktop.DBus.Peer interface.
Properties The standard org.freedesktop.DBus.Properties interface that can be implemented by bus objects to expose a generic "setter/getter" inteface for user-defined properties on DBus.
 

Enum Summary
DBusProxyObj.ReleaseNameResult DBusProxyObj.ReleaseName(String) return value.
DBusProxyObj.RequestNameResult DBusProxyObj.RequestName(String, int) return value.
DBusProxyObj.StartServiceByNameResult DBusProxyObj.StartServiceByName(String, int) return value.
 

Package org.alljoyn.bus.ifaces Description

This package contains various standard AllJoyn interfaces.
